## Operator — on carson / registrar

- Pick a webhook destination (Discord channel webhook / ntfy topic / Telegram bot URL / ...), then add to `/etc/tokenstork/env`:
  ```
  REPORT_WEBHOOK_URL=...
  REPORT_WEBHOOK_SECRET=<optional-shared-secret>
  ```
  then `sudo /opt/tokenstork/infra/redeploy.sh` again (or just `sudo systemctl restart tokenstork.service`).
- Dismiss the test report afterwards:
  ```sql
  UPDATE token_reports SET status='dismissed', reviewed_at=now(), moderator_note='deploy smoke test'
   WHERE details = 'deploy smoke test — please ignore';
  ```
- CF: transfer `tokenstork.com` to Cloudflare as registrar.
- Copy `/etc/tokenstork/env` into the password manager (one-off, high blast-radius on loss).

