## Content + polish

- Better logos for Tapswap, Fex, Cauldron.
- Major information update on bchworks.com (use claude-chrome).
- Custom 404 page.
- Normalize empty-string BCMR `name` to `NULL` at upsert time in [workers/src/bin/bcmr.rs](workers/src/bin/bcmr.rs). Today stored as `''` and defended against in SQL.
- Future CSP tightening — migrate from Caddyfile CSP (`'unsafe-inline'` on script-src) to `kit.csp { mode: 'hash' }` in [svelte.config.js](svelte.config.js) so SvelteKit advertises SHA-256 of its own inline hydration script.
- Fuzzy search using the existing `token_metadata_name_trgm` index — `ORDER BY similarity(name, $q) DESC` with a minimum-score cutoff so "grm" matches "GRIM" and "suhi" matches "sushi". Optional step-up from the current ILIKE.
- Update `package.json` version to `0.1.0` once the ecosystem dashboard expansion ships.
- Migrations framework / runner (deferred until we need a multi-step schema change — today `db/schema.sql` idempotent is enough).
- Regular sync of the TokenStork BCMR registry with OTR.
- Integrate the TokenStork BCMR registry into the site.
- Phase 4c — on-chain BCMR walker (`bcmr_revision` audit column). Deferred unless Paytaca becomes unreliable.

